---
title: Cheesy Loaded Sausages in Buns with Sticky Onions, Paprika Wedges and Rocket
description: Indulge in some nostalgia with a classic from childhood that's also child-friendly! These Cheesy Loaded Sausages in Buns are a grown-up version of summer hot dogs. For little ones, leave off the paprika from the wedges and only top with their favourite toppings.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R10_W11_UK_R10403-10_MAIN_F2_low-56215a8c.jpg
